name: La+ Darknesss | Hololive
description:
I am using AbyssOrangeMix2_hard

The LORA hasn't been trained on a specific outfit, but it can come close to her base outfit with the right prompts.

A weight between 0.6-0.9 is recommended, but other weights may also work in certain situations. Just play around with it and use what feels right to you.

The main prompts are "Laplus, La+, Laplus Darknesss and La+ Darknesss".

For other prompts and generation parameters, see the example images.
